  "decision_conditions": [
    "By reason of its design, scale and size, the proposed development would appear unduly excessive and would fail to relate sympathetically or subordinately to the dwelling, appearing overly dominant and adversely altering the character and appearance of the application site and the surrounding area contrary to the aims and objectives of Policy 28 of the Sutton Local Plan 2018 and Supplementary Planning Document 4 - 'Design of Residential Extensions'.",
    "By reason of its excessive depth and proximity to the shared side boundary line to the south, proposed development would result in an adverse impact on the occupiers of 140 Benhill Road in terms of loss of light, outlook and sense of enclosure contrary to Policy 29 of the Sutton Local Plan 2018 and guidance set out in SPD4 'Design of Residential Extensions'."
